title: 9/11 Anniversary, Rep. Carolyn Maloney
itunes:title: 9/11 Anniversary, Rep. Carolyn Maloney
description:
Guests: Morgan Ortagus, State Department Spokesperson, Jeff Powell, Managing Partner and Chief Investment Officer at Polaris Wealth Advisory Group, Boyd Matheson, Former. Chief of Staff for Senator Mike Lee, and Opinion editor for the Deseret News, Basil Smikle, Democratic Strategist and Former Executive Director of the New York State Democratic Party, and Rep. Carolyn Maloney, a democrat representing New York's 12th district.
